data.description: Very Nice Updated HOME in highly sought after Southwyck subdivision in Heart of Pearland ISD! Incredible entertaining area inside and out, with gorgeous back covered huge patio and fenced backyard. Or come on in and enjoy, stunning quartz counters, soaring ceilings, gas assist fireplace, oversized owner's retreat with en-suite bath sporting a separate shower and tub and dual sinks.  Perfect location for Great Shopping, highly rated schools, mecca for restaurants and entertainment! Easy commuting area!  This home has never flooded and has newer HVAC system, solar screens, beautiful flooring, incredible gas range & a great entertaining floorplan flow.  Welcome Home to this quiet neighborhood!  Great low Tax rate in this area as well so book your appointment to see this Beauty before it is taken, you won't be disappointed!
